title: BRIEF-Pharmagest Interactive H1 net income group share rises to 9.3 mln euros
text:
BRIEF-Pharmagest Interactive H1 net income group share rises to 9.3 mln euros Sept 21 
Sept 21 Pharmagest Interactive SA : 
* H1 net income group share of 9.3 million euros ($10.4 million) versus 8.7 million euros a year ago 
* H1 operating income 14.0 million euros versus 13.3 million euros a year ago Source text: bit.ly/1FXOtUP Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8926 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
